{"tid":676477,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★邱達昌坦承有線寬頻客戶難終止合約的問題","createTime":"2018-05-24T11:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T15:12:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dffdba4ebeb664337af0486f12b0277c0d4527b3","tid":676477,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T11:43:14.000Z","msg":"有線寬頻（1097）主席邱達昌表示，今年4月公司寬頻簽約客戶量多於終止合約，是6年來首見，但相信今年虧損將會持續，明年情況則相對樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n邱達昌出席股東會後表示，未來會發展OTT平台，強調新聞是公司強項，未來只會增強不會減弱。至於內容方面會與其他媒體合作，暫時不考慮拍劇，又指對公司有信心，若有需要注資會繼續支持；人手方面以重整及優化架構為主。<br />\n<br />\n邱達昌坦承有線寬頻<span style=\"color: red;\">客戶難終止合約的問題，目前會盡量簡化手續</span>。營運總裁梁淑儀表示，希望今年第四季可公布OTT平台的內容。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/191972/%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E5%AF%AC%E9%A0%BB%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-%E5%B0%87%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95ott%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F191972%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2599%25A7%25E6%2590%258D%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595ott%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0&d=J2oGmjc0TVxNz9Yc%2BhJ3csP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=61ba3223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/191972/%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E5%AF%AC%E9%A0%BB%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-%E5%B0%87%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95ott%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0</a>"},{"pid":"b6d89c2e805838ca79e36c15e810616bc33bbfdd","tid":676477,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"